trans-unit.source: Provides a type converter that retrieves a list of control IDs in the current container.
trans-unit.target: Gir et typen konverteringsprogram som henter en liste over kontroll IDer i den gjeldende beholderen.

trans-unit.source: The UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter class derives from the <xref:System.ComponentModel.StringConverter> class.
It provides a list of control IDs to be displayed in a property-editing control in design-time environments.
trans-unit.target: Det gir en oversikt over kontroll-IDer som skal vises i en kontroll for redigering av egenskaper i miljøer med utformingen.

trans-unit.source: For more information about type converters, see [How to: Implement a Type Converter](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) and [Generalized Type Conversion](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Du finner mer informasjon om typen konverteringsprogrammer [slik: implementere et konverteringsprogram av typen](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) og [Generalized typekonvertering](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Returns a collection of control IDs from the container inside the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"></xref> object for the specified format context.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en samling av kontrollere IDer fra beholderen i den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.Design.IDesignerHost"> </xref> objektet for den angitte formatet konteksten.

trans-unit.source: A context that can be used for more information about the environment that this converter is invoked from.
trans-unit.target: En kontekst som kan brukes for mer informasjon om miljøet som denne konverteringsprogram kalles fra.

trans-unit.source: This parameter and its properties can be <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Denne parameteren og egenskapene kan være <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: A collection of strings that represent the control IDs of the controls in the current container.
trans-unit.target: En samling av strenger som representerer kontrollen IDer vises i den gjeldende beholderen.

trans-unit.source: If no controls are currently in the container, the method returns an empty collection.
trans-unit.target: Hvis ingen kontroller er i beholderen, returneres en tom samling.

trans-unit.source: If the context is <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref> or if there is no current container, the method returns <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Hvis konteksten <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref> eller hvis det er ingen gjeldende beholderen, returneres <xref uid="langword_csharp_null" name="null" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value that indicates whether the collection of standard values that is returned from <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*> is an exclusive list of possible values for the specified context.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om samlingen av standard verdier som er returnert fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*>er en spesiell liste over mulige verdier for den angitte konteksten.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*>

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection> returned from <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*> is an exclusive list of possible values; <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref> if other values are possible.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection>returnert fra <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*>er en spesiell liste over mulige verdier. <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref> Hvis andre verdier er mulig.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*> </xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeConverter.StandardValuesCollection>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
Returns a value that indicates whether this converter supports a set of control ID values that can be selected from a list.
trans-unit.target: Returnerer en verdi som angir om denne konverteringsprogram støtter en rekke kontrollen ID-verdier som kan velges fra en liste.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*> should be called to find a common set of control ID values the object supports; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Hvis <xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*>skal kall til å søke etter et vanlig sett med kontrollen ID objektet støtter; ellers, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.</xref:System.Web.UI.Design.UpdateProgressAssociatedUpdatePanelIDConverter.GetStandardValues*>

trans-unit.source: The default is <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>.
